verbose_text: We have sought to determine (i) whether angiogenin is detectable in CSF, (ii) whether there is a consistent relationship between plasma and CSF angiogenin levels, (iii) whether genetic variations in the ANG locus control angiogenin expression, and (iv) whether, as has been reported for VEGF XREF_BIBR - XREF_BIBR, there is a dysregulation of angiogenin in sporadic ALS.
